{"tid":425080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(杯葛失敗?) 王晶《追龍》香港票房報捷","createTime":"2017-10-05T11:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T21:46:03.000Z","uid":134071,"like":7,"dislike":68,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"0f4615d24d7938b35b8cf5986538f36a44c8b78c","tid":425080,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T11:39:31.000Z","msg":"香港觀眾始終都係愛惜王晶....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1507183237434&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20171005\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1507183237434%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20171005&d=Iu%2FBuLPgulX4A9HLbgDzudtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a02bdc37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1507183237434%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20171005&h=7f9b6f18\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1507183237434&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20171005</a><br />\n<br />\n【開畫7日收千萬】《追龍》港澳票房報捷 劉德華賞月慶祝 (14:25)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨晚中秋夜，劉德華在官方網誌上載燈籠及月亮相，並以「賞月」為題，寫下簡單一句「你心我心」。<br />\n<br />\n他跟甄子丹演出的電影《追龍》於港澳兩地上映近一星期，票房已直逼1000萬﹗電影不但成為新加坡、馬來西亞及台灣的開畫票房冠軍，在內地更錄下5天破2.5億港元的佳績。<br />\n<br />\n《追龍》將上世紀60至70年代的九龍城寨搭建出來。甄子丹說︰「九龍城寨是黑幫片的地標，能夠將九龍城寨搭建出來，能重拾昔日香港黑幫片的情懷﹗」劉德華雖然是客串演出，但他每日完成拍攝後都會留下來跟劇組研究劇本及製作。<br />\n<br />\n（即時娛樂）"},{"pid":"3f033c524f6b33f10a28d95537834c33b8ed7183","tid":425080,"uid":53687,"like":2,"dislike":29,"score":-27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T11:43:09.000Z","msg":"想睇華仔同宇宙最強啫"},{"pid":"2791618870512c10cb81865353c4684c5cdb410f","tid":425080,"uid":39365,"like":10,"dislike":10,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T11:46:53.000Z","msg":"有咁既陣容七日只收一千萬其實係失敗囉,只不過無戰狼2輸得咁慘"},{"pid":"29984d60ec8995e157e85112c776aaf9da4df938","tid":425080,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T11:52:02.000Z","msg":"港澳兩地上映加埋1000萬,淨香港幾多?"},{"pid":"cc26ba409c83e083bf87f4fd146f87cfd6b68400","tid"